        <p><strong>Robert, age 64 — founder of SnapProtein.</strong> I weigh around 200 lbs. I spent years thinking 90–100g of protein was a solid target. When I actually ran the numbers, I was below my floor — not at my goal. This post is the math I wish someone had shown me earlier.</p>
