        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mm-row">
        <div class="mm-meal"><strong>Lunch</strong>Turkey sandwich + side salad</div>
        <div>
          <div class="mm-g short">~25g</div>
          <div class="mm-verdict bad">⚠ Catabolic — Muscle Wasting</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mm-row">
        <div class="mm-meal"><strong>Snack</strong>Handful of nuts + apple</div>
        <div>
          <div class="mm-g short">~7g</div>
          <div class="mm-verdict bad">⚠ Catabolic — Muscle Wasting</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="mm-row">
        <div class="mm-meal"><strong>Dinner</strong>5oz chicken breast + vegetables + rice</div>
        <div>
          <div class="mm-g ok">~44g</div>
